				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Giao/D%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0i/poem-5L018kZgEYOg9TKvoONAqA">Dạ hoài - 夜懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Giao/author-VVl3mnm6-DXAxMiEF4IPnw">Nguyễn Văn Giao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Du-Th%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90inh-s%C6%A1n/poem-pJAWo0CNtnx6Y8n62FZrxg">Du Thần Đinh sơn - 遊神丁山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-Th%C3%BAc-Thuy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-h%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-v%C5%A9-h%E1%BA%ADu-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-v%C3%A3n-di%E1%BB%83u-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-JAp1roXRwtzC0w6FPLw3-w">Hoạ thượng thư Thúc Thuyên đệ hạ nhật vũ hậu lương đình vãn diểu nguyên vận - 和尚書叔荃弟夏日雨後涼亭晚眺原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-H%E1%BB%8Dc-Thuy%C3%AAn/Ho%E1%BA%A1-V%C4%83n-Ph%E1%BA%A1m/poem-4LUWzNerM6tfkx3QhWpc2g">Hoạ Văn Phạm - 和聞梵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-H%E1%BB%8Dc-Thuy%C3%AAn/author-ZG1snfgbwBOBCSAnwp2z4w">Tào Học Thuyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ph%E1%BB%93n/Lu%E1%BA%ADn-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-gNyuXuF7yPPhB-huS3ehnQ">Luận thi kỳ 1 - 論詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ph%E1%BB%93n/author-5gmuZmguwm6161F8wvDGRQ">Triệu Phồn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ng%C6%B0-%C3%B4ng/poem--njiBhIsA-zBGeDDm_k3TA">Ngư ông - 漁翁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Thu%E1%BB%B7-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-n2jCNzT17fugYXAO61bmbw">Thuỷ liễu - 水柳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/Th%E1%BB%AD-th%E1%BB%9Di-v%C3%B4-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-k%E1%BB%87/poem-O4p7auGiXdbTM7sWHPVmYA">Thử thời vô thường kệ - 此時無常偈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/author-9I32ODUXRXPuHHWWFnp0IQ">Trần Thái Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/Trung-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ch%C3%BAc-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-Ta42ps0UvzKjr5-vMIZ4jQ">Trung nhật chúc hương - 中日祝香</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/author-9I32ODUXRXPuHHWWFnp0IQ">Trần Thái Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%E1%BA%A1p-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-gTIlgBSifscJ7KC8jnsydw">Xuân nhật tạp hứng - 春日雜興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
